entry.title: WebNN: Define the TensorDesc for DirectML backend
entry.content:
This CL defines the TensorDesc class to wrap a tensor description

(DML_TENSOR_DESC) needed by a DML graph. It owns the tensor's

dimensions, strides and DML_BUFFER_TENSOR_DESC. The TensorDesc will

be used for building a DML graph's description (DML_GRAPH_DESC).



This CL adds utils files to host the helper methods for DML backend

and also adds the WebNNTensorDescTest test cases.



Based on these changes, the command_recorder_test.cc has been

refactored and simplified.
